# Scenario: All comparison operators
# Why: Validates that _gt, _gte, _lt, and _lte suffixes are correctly mapped to their respective RQL infix operators.
query 'CALL graphql::explain("query { transactions(where: { block_gt: 10, block_gte: 11, index_lt: 5, index_lte: 4 }) { hash } }")'
---
> +-------+----------+----------------+
> |  idx  |   kind   |     detail     |
> +-------+----------+----------------+
> |   0   |   From   |  transactions  |
> |   1   |  Filter  |   block > 10   |
> |   2   |  Filter  |  block >= 11   |
> |   3   |  Filter  |   index < 5    |
> |   4   |  Filter  |   index <= 4   |
> |   5   |   Map    |      hash      |
> +-------+----------+----------------+
>
